Docker container for Disco
==========================

http://www.docker.io/


Building
========

 $ docker build -t disco/disco .


Running
======

For example:

 $ docker run -p 8989:8989 -t -i disco/disco

 and point your browser to http://localhost:8989


More
====

A SSH server is running, you can reach it by adding a -p. Default
password is 'disco'.
